<h1>Overlay nameserver - BIND name server</h1>
<p>Supplies the <a href="https://www.isc.org/bind/">BIND</a> nameserver.</p>
<p>To set up a simple caching-only nameserver, copy the file
<code>/etc/named-cache.conf</code> to <code>/etc/named.conf</code>,
modifying as appropriate (you may need to update the local subnet in the
<code>allow-query</code> statement) and start the server with</p>
<pre>
svcadm enable named
</pre>
